            "title": "美股崩、台股慘？這些股票卻逆勢狂飆100%！",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>★總經環境影響台股表現★</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"383\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.9843342036553524\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/m/fbee761fd1f6d87c8af6ae16fb7918f1.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/fbee761fd1f6d87c8af6ae16fb7918f1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/fbee761fd1f6d87c8af6ae16fb7918f1.jpg 1x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/xl/fbee761fd1f6d87c8af6ae16fb7918f1.jpg 2x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/xxl/fbee761fd1f6d87c8af6ae16fb7918f1.jpg 3x\"/></figure></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國 2 月非農新增就業 15.1 萬，低於預期 16 萬，失業率升至 4.1%，經濟數據不佳。聯準會主席鮑爾暫不急於降息，加上川普關稅政策不確定性，美股維持低檔震盪，拖累台股測試 22000 點支撐，不過台灣 2 月出口 413.1 億美元，創歷史同期新高，顯示基本面穩健。下週 AI 類股如台積電、廣達公佈營收，數據亮眼，可望帶動市場反彈。短線台股維持 22000-23500 點區間震盪，投資焦點應轉向個股表現。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>★<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>指數比<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>更影響台股★</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"348\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.9827586206896552\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/m/ab209506581b9aba8145db949d9f9a57.jpg\" data-width=\"690\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/ab209506581b9aba8145db949d9f9a57.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>相較於<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數對台股影響更大，成分股包含台積電 ADR 與輝達，台股與<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>指數相關係數高達 0.81。台股止跌關鍵應關注<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>指數反彈及台積電能否守住 1000 元整數關卡，若下週三美國 CPI 數據若符合預期，則有望帶動市場反彈。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>★這些股票逆勢狂飆 100%！★</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"383\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.9843342036553524\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/m/f6650326cf3490b8137be977165e8100.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/f6650326cf3490b8137be977165e8100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/f6650326cf3490b8137be977165e8100.jpg 1x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/xl/f6650326cf3490b8137be977165e8100.jpg 2x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/xxl/f6650326cf3490b8137be977165e8100.jpg 3x\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"383\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.9843342036553524\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/m/9eb4b79b129ec8cdf512736174cbee3b.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/9eb4b79b129ec8cdf512736174cbee3b.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/l/9eb4b79b129ec8cdf512736174cbee3b.jpg 1x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/xl/9eb4b79b129ec8cdf512736174cbee3b.jpg 2x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5889999/xxl/9eb4b79b129ec8cdf512736174cbee3b.jpg 3x\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大盤震盪整理，市場信心不足，但部分具特殊題材的中小型股漲幅已達 50-100%，譬如 LINE PAY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7722:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7722\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7722-TW</a>)受惠電子支付滲透率提升，股價自 426 元飆升至 932 元，三個月內漲幅 118%；辣椒 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4946:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4946\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4946-TW</a>) 代理手遊《大航海時代》，1 月營收年增 1498.8%，2 月年增 817.3%，股價自 40 元短短一個半月內飆升至 85.9 元，漲幅 114%。擁有相同特徵的 5 檔股票，值得留意：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>智捷 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8176:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8176\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8176-TW</a>)、華泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2329:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2329\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2329-TW</a>)、亞信 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3169:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3169\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3169-TW</a>)、世紀鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9958-TW</a>)、德淵 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4720:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4720\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4720-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"270\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"2.814814814814815\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cn